data.text:
Investment ManagersFinance

Stevens Capital Management LP (SCM) is a SEC-registered investment advisor and hedge fund manager headquartered in Radnor, Pennsylvania. The firm was founded by Matthew S. Tewksbury in 2002 and is a subsidiary of Adams Holdings LLC. SCM provides investment services to private investment vehicles. Investors may include high net-worth individuals, employees or individuals affiliated with SCM, trusts, partnerships, corporations and other business entities.

Food DistributorsDistribution Services

Frozen Value Ltd. offers frozen foods. Its products include premium branded frozen foods, dry grocery products and groceries. The company was founded by Jack Fulton in 1960 and is headquartered in Darton, the United Kingdom.

Investment ManagersFinance

Offit Capital Advisors LLC (Offit Capital) is an independent, SEC-registered investment adviser headquartered in New York City. The firm was founded by Morris Offit in 2017. Offit Capital provides customized investment advisory services to wealthy individuals, multi-generational families, endowments and foundations.

Other Consumer ServicesConsumer Services

University of Southern California is a private research university that mainly offers undergraduate, graduate & other higher education. The university was founded in 1880 and is headquartered in Los Angeles, CA.

Hospital/Nursing ManagementHealth Services

Memorial Sloan-Kettering Cancer Center operates as a private cancer center. It offers cancer care services to adult; and child and teen patients. Its services include risk assessment and screening; diagnosis and treatment; clinical trials; patient and caregiver education; and pediatric clinical trials. The company was founded by John J. Astor and Charlotte Astor in 1884 and is headquartered in New York, NY.

Internet Software/ServicesTechnology Services

Rome2rio Pty Ltd. operates an online travel search engine. The firm operates as a global trip planner that helps you get from a to b worldwide. The company was founded by Bernhard Tschirren and Michael Cameron in 2010 and is headquartered in Melbourne, Australia.

Investment ManagersFinance

Morgan Stanley AIP GP LP (AIP) is a SEC-registered investment advisor and funds-of-hedge funds manager headquartered in West Conshohocken, Pennsylvania. The firm is a subsidiary of Morgan Stanley Investment Management, Inc. and their ultimate parent is Morgan Stanley (NYSE: MS). AIP generally provides investment advice to registered and unregistered investment companies, pooled investment vehicles, separate accounts, funds of one, corporate/business entities, high net-worth individuals, endowments, foundations, charitable institutions, sovereign wealth funds, foreign regulated funds such as UCITs, pension plans and domestic and foreign government agencies, and trusts. In addition, the firm, through its Hedge Fund Solutions business, provides hedge fund manager research services to Morgan Stanley Smith Barney LLC (MSSB).
